\begin_layout Proof
The proof is by contradiction.
 Assume the proposition is false.
 Then,
 for a risky asset level 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

 (where 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{D}(B)\neq\emptyset$
\end_inset

),
